description: The victim, a nine-year-old girl, was kidnapped and attacked in Villiers in western France.
title: Two men arrested over rape of nine-year-old girl in rural France
title_page: Two men arrested over rape of nine-year-old girl in rural France - BBC News
maintext: The girl was found shortly after she went missing and was taken to Poitiers University Hospital, where she is still being cared for.
